'''劉陳昭玲'''（{{Lang-nan-tw|Lâu Tân Tsiau-lîn}}，{{Bd|1956年|6月18日}}）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.phcouncil.gov.tw/mop2.php?no=M06030004|title=澎湖縣議會 議員介紹|accessdate=2019-03-16|author=|date=2018-12-25|publisher=澎湖縣議會全球資訊網|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2019-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604171700/http://www.phcouncil.gov.tw/mop2.php?no=M06030004|dead-url=no}}</ref>，原名'''陳昭玲'''，[[中國國民黨|中國國民黨]]籍政治人物，第15屆至第19屆澎湖縣議會議長。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181225/1489598/|title=〈澎議會選舉　國民黨劉陳昭玲議長五連霸〉|author=|date=2018-12-25|work=|accessdate=2019-03-16|newspaper=蘋果日報|first=逸民|last=許|language=zh-tw}}</ref>

== 生平 ==
劉陳昭玲出生於澎湖縣[[湖西鄉|湖西鄉]][[沙港村|沙港村]]，幼年家境清貧，舉凡下田餵豬、照顧弟妹，皆親力親為。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20141130001673-260102?chdtv|title=〈劉陳昭玲 化身澎政壇新掌門〉|author=|date=2014-11-30|work=|publisher=|accessdate=2019-05-25|language=zh-tw|format=|first=可文|last=陳|newspaper=中國時報|archive-date=2019-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190613122334/https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20141130001673-260102?chdtv|dead-url=no}}</ref>

自25歲投入[[澎湖縣議會|澎湖縣議會]]選舉<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.penghutimes.com/ph/%E5%8A%89%E9%99%B3%E6%98%AD%E7%8E%B2%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8-%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%BF%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF%E7%9B%B8%E6%8C%BA|title=〈劉陳昭玲登記參選 夫婿一路相挺〉|author=|date=2018-08-31|work=|accessdate=2019-03-16|last=鄒|first=秀成|newspaper=澎湖時報|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629113044/http://www.penghutimes.com/ph/%e5%8a%89%e9%99%b3%e6%98%ad%e7%8e%b2%e7%99%bb%e8%a8%98%e5%8f%83%e9%81%b8-%e5%a4%ab%e5%a9%bf%e4%b8%80%e8%b7%af%e7%9b%b8%e6%8c%ba|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，創下連十屆當選、未曾落選的紀錄。<ref name=":0" />

2021年8月10日，劉陳昭玲以議長身份下鄉赴往湖西鄉考察，認為湖西鄉太多保安林，嚴重妨礙地區建設與發展，要求[[行政院農業委員會林務局|林務局]]與農漁局盡速解編，以[[BOT模式|BOT]]方式吸引民間投資，並要求澎湖縣政府建設處的[[林投公園|林投黃金沙灘]]開發案，投資金額需至少新台幣12億、履約保證金至少6000萬元，如此規模的開發案才能促進地方繁榮。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://penghudaily.blogspot.com/2021/08/blog-post_6530.html|title=〈 劉陳昭玲不滿要求解編保安林 怒嗆林務局「別站茅坑不拉屎」 〉|author=鄭家瑜|publisher=澎湖日報|date=2021-08-11|language=zh-tw|archivedate=2021-08-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210811160220/https://penghudaily.blogspot.com/2021/08/blog-post_6530.html|accessdate=2021-08-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 家族 ==
[[File:烏崁漁港_Wukan_Fishing_Harbor_10.jpg|左]]
* 丈夫劉崇保乃澎湖商界巨擎，轄有長勇營造、泰永企業行分別是營造業與建材批發的行號<ref>{{Cite web|title=【綜合營造業】長勇營造工程有限公司|url=https://www.ezsogosi.com/company/information/4fbc0b20|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=Ez搜公司|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2019-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190525130300/https://www.ezsogosi.com/company/information/4fbc0b20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=【建材批發業】泰永企業行|url=https://www.ezsogosi.com/company/information/fbfb8a54|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=Ez搜公司|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2019-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190525130259/https://www.ezsogosi.com/company/information/fbfb8a54|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亦是澎南汽車貨運行的負責人<ref>{{Cite web|title=【汽車貨櫃貨運業】澎南汽車貨運行|url=https://www.ezsogosi.com/company/information/ccc1ea6b|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=Ez搜公司|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2019-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190525130259/https://www.ezsogosi.com/company/information/ccc1ea6b|dead-url=no}}</ref>與保有商投菸酒食材批發業的代表人<ref>{{Cite web|title=【建材批發業】保有商投有限公司|url=https://www.ezsogosi.com/company/information/a5bd1421|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=Ez搜公司|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2019-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190525130258/https://www.ezsogosi.com/company/information/a5bd1421|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*[[澎湖縣農會|澎湖縣農會]]總幹事陳一正為劉陳昭玲胞弟。<ref name=":3">{{Cite news|url=http://www.penghutimes.com/modules/phnews/index.php?nsn=25275|title=〈議長母親陳太夫人公祭 各方弔唁 備極哀榮〉|author=|date=2018-07-22|work=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=zh-tw|format=|last=鄒|first=秀成|newspaper=澎湖時報|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924133740/http://www.penghutimes.com/modules/phnews/index.php?nsn=25275|dead-url=no}}</ref>

